embeds.description:
Welcome to the private chat area for VES Section members.

All of these Section channels are  accessible by all VES members from all VES Sections.  Feel free to use the individual Sections channels to network with locals, plan, brainstorm, etc. or post in other channels to reach out and work with members of other sections.

Please drop suggestions or feature requests in the #suggestions channel below.  We'll add new Section channels as needed/requested.
